# Security

## Environment

- `.env` is gitignored — never commit it
- EmailJS keys only via `import.meta.env.VITE_EMAILJS_*`
- Do not add hardcoded fallback service IDs or API keys in `Contact.jsx`

## Contact form

- If env vars are missing, show a clear user-facing error; do not send with placeholder keys

## Git

- Hooks may block destructive commands (`git push --force`, `git reset --hard`)
- Do not commit files matching `.env` or secret patterns

## DECISION_LOG

- Record decisions only; never paste secret values
